JONAS: Now, you weren't able to actually control your powers when you were up against those two muggers.

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:58.100
Why do you think that was?

00:03:58.100 --> 00:04:01.300
-It was the first time I ever had to use them for real.

00:04:01.300 --> 00:04:05.000
Performance anxiety, maybe?
-Or was it that cheap champagne you were wino'ing?

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:08.500
-You think my super weakness is alcohol?
-We have no idea.

00:04:08.500 --> 00:04:13.000
-DUDE! That would suck.
